analysis: The agent omitted the required "contactMethod": "Email" parameter in its call to SNE_MS, resulting in a function call that did not match the expected input and failing to specify the contact method as instructed.

The agent used title-case values ("Emerging", "Moderate", "Dynamic") for function parameters instead of the required lowercase format ("emerging", "moderate", "dynamic"), causing a parameter mismatch and the evaluator to not recognize the function call as correct.

The agent incorrectly set the "outputDetail" parameter to "Detailed" instead of the expected "Summary" value, resulting in a parameter mismatch and failure to produce the required function call signature.

The agent incorrectly added an unsupported "weatherDetail" argument to the FS_FAW function call, resulting in a parameter mismatch and failure to match the expected function signature. Only "airportCode" and "flightNumber" should be included.

The agent called the correct function (GF_UIFG) with the correct interest ("Sci-Fi") but omitted the required "ratingThreshold": "good" parameter, failing to constrain recommendations by rating as specified in the user request.

The agent incorrectly mapped the qualitative rating "high" to a numeric value "4.5" for the "rating" parameter instead of using the expected categorical string "high," leading to a function call mismatch.
